   Máńgi ómirge ıe bolady

[V2]
 Men Iemizdi kútem(in)
 Onyń sózine senem
 Raqymmen qutqaryldym
 Raqymmen bosa-atyldym

[B1]
   Óte qundy qan
   Meni bosatty
   Barlyq ma-aqtaý Isaǵa
   Bárin tapsyram
   Tek saǵan Isa
   Meniń Qutqarýshym

[P1]
   Máńgi ómirge ıe bolady</lyrics>
